;[What's New in Firefox] It's now easier and faster to get where you want to go with the latest Firefox.
[Na tha ùr ann am Firefox] Ruigidh am Firefox as ùire do cheann-uidhe nas luaithe agus air dòigh nas fhasa a-nis.


;With the redesigned Home page you can now easily access and navigate to your most commonly used menu options.
Chaidh an duilleag-mhòr ath-dhealbhadh agus tha e nas fhasa a-nis cothrom fhaighinn air na pìosan dhen chlàr-taice a chleachdas tu gu tric.


;Like downloads, bookmarks, history, add-ons, sync and settings.
Can na luchdaich thu a-nuas, na comharran-lìn, an eachdraidh, na tuilleadain, an sioncronachadh 's na roghainnean.


;[New Tab Page] We've also added improvements to your New Tab page.
[Duilleag taba ùr] Leasaich sinn duillean nan tabaichean ùra cuideachd.


;With the New Tab page, you can now easily navigate to your most recent and frequently visited sites in one click.
Tha e furasta le duilleag nan tabaichean ùra cothrom fhaighinn air na làraichean a thadhail thu orra gu tric o chionn goirid le aon bhriogadh.


;To start using the New Tab page, create a new tab by clicking the '+' at the top of your browser.
Ma tha thu airson duilleag nan tabaichean ùra a chleachdadh, cruthaich taba 's tu a' briogadh air a + aig barr a' bhrabhsair agad.


;The New Tab page will now display thumbnails of your most recently and frequently visited websites from your Awesome Bar history.
Chì thu dealbhagan dhe na làraichean-lìn air an do thadhail thu gu tric o chionn goirid (stèidhichte air eachdraidh an t-sàr-bhàir agad) air duilleag nan tabaichean ùra.


;You can customize your New Tab page by dragging the thumbnails around to change the order.
'S urrainn dhut duilleag nan tabaichean ùra a ghnàthachadh ma shlaodas tu mun cuairt iad.


;Click on the pushpin to lock the site into place, or the 'X' button to remove a site.
Briog air a' phrìne gus làrach a ghlasadh san ìate sin no air an X gus làrach a thoirt air falbh.


;You can also click the 'grid' icon in the top right of the page to go back to the blank new Tab page.
'S urrainn dhut briogadh air a' ghriod bheag aig barr na duilleige air an làimh dheas gus duilleag bhàn nan tabaichean ùra a ruigsinn.


;Get the latest Firefox now and start using these new features today!
Faigh greim air a' Firefox as ùire an-dràsta 's faigh cothrom air na feartan ùra seo an-diugh!
